# ============================================================================
# Supabase RAG Configuration Example
# ============================================================================
# Add these variables to your .env file to enable RAG with Supabase pgvector
# ============================================================================

# Supabase Configuration (Required for RAG)
SUPABASE_URL=https://oveixhmndwrtymuymdxm.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key_here  # Same as above

# OpenAI Configuration (Required for embeddings)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# ============================================================================
# How to get these values:
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. SUPABASE_URL:
#    - Go to https://supabase.com/dashboard
#    - Select your project
#    - Go to Settings > API
#    - Copy "Project URL"
#
# 2. SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY / SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY:
#    - Same location (Settings > API)
#    - Copy "service_role" key (NOT the "anon" key)
#    - Use the same value for both variables
#    - IMPORTANT: Keep this secret! Never commit to git
#
# 3. OPENAI_API_KEY:
#    - Go to https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#    - Create a new API key
#    - Copy and paste here
#
# ============================================================================
# After adding these variables:
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Execute the SQL script in Supabase:
#    - Open Supabase SQL Editor
#    - Run scripts/supabase_pgvector_schema.sql
#
# 2. Restart your API server:
#    cd apps/api
#    python -m uvicorn src.main:app --reload --port 8000
#
# 3. Check logs for:
#    "RAG service initialized with Supabase"
#
# 4. Test the upload endpoint:
#    curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/rag/upload \
#      -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
#      -F "files=@document.pdf"
#
# ============================================================================
